name: Brian Gary
description: I’m a very cheerful and fun to be with. i understand people and things for what there are and am good looking and very understanding. I’m used to driving 45 minutes to meet friends for breakfast, a movie, a book signing, a lunch meeting, etc. My ego isn’t so big that I believe the perfect partner has been strategically placed within 20 miles of my physical location, regardless of that physical location in the world.
